hat averaging in grid cells performs equally well. We find that for a\nsurvey such as 6dFGSv we can estimate sigma_8 with less than 3% bias from\nnonlinearities. The expected error on sigma_8 after marginalising over Omega_m\nis approximately 16 percent.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 13 Feb 2008 22:49:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 2 Jul 2008 17:47:11 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 3 Nov 2008 10:53:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
