ging flux and the pre-existing\nmagnetic loop proceeds in an intermittent, probably quasi-periodic, way.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 14 Feb 2008 04:35:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
